name: TRIP REPORT | Swoop Airlines Boeing 737-800 Abbotsford to Edmonton
description:
In August last year, I flew on Swoop Airlines, one of several new ultra-low-cost carriers in Canada, on a round trip from Edmonton to Abbotsford for just $120.

Here's the return flight, flying on Swoop's fourth 737-800, C-FONK, on Swoop #124. See what I thought of WestJet's ultra-low-cost subsidiary in this video!
